description: Yum Yum Concessions is a fun concessions stand on wheels, serving the best kettle corn, pork rinds and fresh squeeze lemonade in Hampton Roads, VA. This food truck is a great addition for any event, delicious finger snacks that are perfect way to start a celebration or treat after a long day. With a large selection of flavored kettle corn there is something for everyones crunch on.
name: Yum Yum Consessions
